==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===
* Able to perform night battle special attacks without night operations personnel at Kai Ni E.
* Able to freely convert between Kai Ni and Kai Ni E.
** When converting, you need to pay the full resource cost again.
** You will not need additional blueprints and prototype catapults.

===Overview===
'''Kai'''
* Decent firepower, middle of the pack for a carrier.
* Decent HP and armour, slightly above average for a carrier.
* Good slot count.
* Bad slot distribution. But single large slot allows for one powerful airstrike.  

'''Kai Ni'''  
* Decent firepower for a carrier.
* Decent HP and armour.
* Good slot count.
* Bad slot distribution. But single large slot allows for one powerful airstrike. 

'''Kai Ni E'''
* Good firepower for a carrier.
* Decent HP and armour.
* Decent slot count.
* Bad slot distribution. But single large slot allows for one powerful airstrike.
* Gains the Ability to attack at night without needing [[Night Operation Aviation Personnel]] when equipped with night-capable planes

